quran[88]{c,v,t}:
  28,1,"Taa, Siin, Miim."
  28,2,"ﾆ各e ko aayeeje deftere ﾉ殿nngunde nden."
  28,3,"Moﾉ容n janngira e maaﾉ預 hoore goonga, kumpital Muusaa e Fir'awna, wonan'de yimﾉ兎 gooﾅ極擁nooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  28,4,"Pellet, Fir'awna townitino ka leydi; o waﾉ擁 yimﾉ兎 mayri ndin pecce-pecce: homo lo'ina fedde goo e maﾉ橡兎, o hirsa ﾉ妬ﾉ橡兎 maﾉ橡兎 worﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n o acca rewﾉ兎 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n. Pellet, ko e bonnooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n o jiyanoo."
  28,5,"Miﾉ容n faandinoo moﾆｴﾆｴagol e lo'inanooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ka leydi; Min mbaﾉ預 ﾉ兎 koohooﾉ兎, Min mbaﾉ預 ﾉ兎 kadi ronooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  28,6,"Min kuﾉ妬ndina ﾉ兎 e leydi ndin, Min kolla Fir'awna e Haamaana e koneeli maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n, kon ko ﾉ兎 kulaynoo."
  28,7,"Min mbhayini e yumma Muusaa, wonn'de: ""Muynin mo"". Si a hulanoyii mo, ko yo a bugoyo mo ka maayo. Wata a hulu, wata a suno; pellet, Men ruttay mo ka maaﾉ預, Min mbﾉ熔ya mo gooto e Nulaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n""."
  28,8,"Yimﾉ兎 Fir'awna ﾉ兎n kocci mo, fii yo laatano ﾉ兎 gaﾃｱo e suno. Pellet, Fir'awna e Haamaana e koneeli maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n, ﾉ兎 laatino woopﾉ兎."
  28,9,"Debbo Fir'awna on wi'i: ""(Kun entum ko) ﾉ砥uﾉ兎endi gite am e an kadi! Wota on war mo, hino gasa ka o nafata en, maa jogitoren mo ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔"". Hari ﾉ兎 so'aani."
  28,10,"ﾆ‘rnde yumma Muusaa nden wonti yeewnde. Haa o eﾉ橡妬 feﾃｱﾃｱin'de fii makko, si wonaano Min tabintinnde ﾉ兎rnde makko nden, fii yo o laato e gooﾅ極擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  28,11,"[Yumma Muusaa] wi'ani banndiraawo makko on: ""Jokkitu mo""; o haynii mo ka de'estii, ﾉ兎 so'aa-anndude."
  28,12,"Min karminani mo ko adii, (enﾉ擁) muynirﾉ擁 ﾉ擁n, (banndiraawo makko on) mbi'i: ""On ngaccat mi tinndina on fii yimﾉ兎 suudu, ﾉ兎 ne'ana on mo, hara kadi ko laaﾉ殿nat ﾉ兎 mo?"""
  28,13,"Min ndtti mo ka yumma makko, fii yo ﾉ兎rnde makko ﾉ砥uﾉ砥, hara o sunaaki, e fii yo o anndu pellet, fodoore Alla nden, ko goonga. Kono ﾉ砥rﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉de e maﾉ橡兎 ngaanndaa."
  28,14,"Nde o yottinoo sagatalaaku makko ngun, o fotondi- ri, Min ngokki mo faamu e ganndal. Ko wano non Min njoﾉ妬rta moﾆｴﾆｴinooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  28,15,"O naatiri e saare nden, feewndo welsindaare yimﾉ兎 mayre; o tawi worﾉ兎 ﾉ擁ﾉ熔 no haﾉ殿 ton: goﾉ遼熔 on ko jiyaaﾉ熔 e leﾃｱol makko, oya on ko jiyaaﾉ熔 e ayﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n. Jeyaaﾉ熔 e leﾃｱol makko ngol ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬ri faabo e hoore jiyaaﾉ熔 e gaﾃｱo makko on. Muusaa uttii mo, nde gayni fii makko. [Muusaa] maaki: ""ﾆ隔m ﾉ熔o, ko jiyaaﾉ蓉m e kuuﾉ容 seytaane. Pellet, ko o gaﾃｱo, majjinoowo ﾉ殿nnguﾉ熔""."
  28,16,"O maaki: ""Joomi am, mi tooﾃｱii hoore-am; haforanam."" O haforani mo. Pellet, ko Kaﾅ橘o woni Haforoowo, jurmotooﾉ熔 On."
  28,17,"O maaki: ""Joomi am, sabu ko neeminﾉ預a ko e am, mi wonataa ballo bomﾉ兎 ﾉ兎""."
  28,18,"O wonti kulﾉ熔 ka saare, homo habbii [nanngeede]. Tawi faabinornooﾉ熔 mo on hanki, homo faabinora mo [hannde kadi]. Muusaa maakani mo: ""Pellet, ko a bewﾉ熔 ﾉ殿nnguﾉ熔""."
  28,19,"Nde Muusaa faandinoo nanngugol tawﾉ熔 on ko gaﾃｱo maﾉ橡兎 kamﾉ兎 ﾉ擁ﾉ熔, o wi'i: ""ey ma yo Muusaa, a faala bargol lam, wano ittirnoﾉ預a woﾅ橘ii non haﾅ橘i? A faandaaki, si wonaa wonugol dunndarankeejo ka leydi, a faandaaki jeyeede e moﾆｴﾆｴinooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎en""."
  28,20,"Gorko iwri ka ﾉ砥ri woﾉ遼蓉de e saare nden, homo yaccoo, o wi'i: ""eey ma Muusaa, mbatu ngun no fewjana fii bargol maa. Yaltu (e leydi ndin). Ko mi jiyaaﾉ熔 e laaﾉ殿nooﾉ兎 ma""."
  28,21,"O yalti ton, ko o kulﾉ熔, himo tijjii [nanngeede]. O maaki: ""Joomi am, danﾉ溶dam e yimﾉ兎 tooﾃｱooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎en""."
  28,22,"Nde o feewtunoo hella Madyana, o maaki: ""Hino hasii ka Joomi am fewnirta lam, e laawol pocciingol ngol""."
  28,23,"Nde o hewtunoo ka ﾉ砥nndu Madyana, o tawi ﾉ熔n dental yimﾉ兎, heﾉ兎 njarna [daabeeji maﾉ橡兎], o tawi gaanin maﾉ橡兎, rewﾉ兎 ﾉ擁ﾉ熔, no sogga [dammi maﾉ橡兎], o maaki: ""Ko holﾉ蓉m habbi-ﾉ熔n?"" ﾆ‘ mb'i: ""Min njarnataa haa aynooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n nde'estoo, baaba amen, ko mawﾉ熔 nayeejo""."
  28,24,"O yarnani ﾉ兎 [dammi ﾉ擁n], refti o huccitiri ka ﾉ熔wdi, o maaki: ""Joomi am, min ko njippinﾉ預a e am woo e moﾆｴﾆｴere, ko mi katonjiﾉ熔""."
  28,25,"Gooto e [jiwﾉ兎] ﾉ兎n ari e makko, homo yahra hersa, o wi'i: ""Baaba am no nodde, fii yo o yoﾉ兎 njoﾉ電i kon ko njarnan-ﾉ預a men"". Tuma o hewtunoo ka [mawﾉ熔] on, o sifanii mo fii [makko], o maaki: ""Wota a hul, a daﾉ擁i yimﾉ兎 tooﾃｱooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n""."
  28,26,"Gooto e [jiwﾉ兎] ﾉ兎n wi'i: ""ﾆｳettu mo golle, yo baaba. Pellet, ko ﾉ砥ri moﾆｴﾆｴude e mo ﾆｴettataa golle, ko doolnuﾉ熔 koolniiﾉ熔""."
  28,27,"[Mawﾉ熔] on maaki: ""Miﾉ熔 yiﾉ擁 desingol ma gooto e jiwﾉ兎 am ﾉ兎n ﾉ熔o ﾉ擁ﾉ熔, e hoore yo a golla-nam duuﾉ妬 jeetati. Si a timminii sappo, haray ko e sago maa; mi faalaaka saﾉ葉inannde ma. A tawat kam, si Alla jaﾉ妬i, ko e moﾆｴﾆｴinooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n mi jeyaa""."
  28,28,"[Muusaa] maaki: ""ﾆ隔m wonii hakkunde am e mon. Happu woo e majji ﾉ擁ﾉ擁, ﾉ擁 mi huuﾉ渡i, haray ﾉ妬ﾉ葉eede alanaa e kam. En waﾉ擁i Alla pawtiiﾉ熔 e ko wowluﾉ容n kon""."
  28,29,"Nde Muusaa timminnoo happu ngun, o yahdi e ﾉ兎ydnuure makko, o haynii yiite ka senngo (fello) Tuuri, o maaki ﾉ兎unguure makko nden: ""ngonee ﾉ熔o, min mi haynike yiite. Mbelejo'o mi addana on e magge kumpital maa te'annde(docotal) yiite ngen, mbelejo'o itworon""."
  28,30,"Nde o heewtunoo nge, o noddiraa ka fonngo ﾃｱaamo aynde, ka tummbere barkinaande, ka (takko) lekki, won'nde: ""eey ma Muusaa! Ko Miin woni Alla, Jeyﾉ熔 winndere nden""."
  28,31,"Kadi: ""Bugo tuggordu maa ndun""; nde o tinunoo hundu dillira wa mboddi,o huccitiri dogudu, o yeﾆｴﾆｴitaaki. [O noddaa]: ""Ko an yo Muusaa! Artu, wota a hul; ko a jiyaaﾉ熔 e hooliiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎en."
  28,32,"Naatnu juungo maa ngon ka jayba maa, ngo yaltat ranewo, ko aldaa e ﾃｱawu. Bakaa e maaﾉ預, juuﾉ容 maa ﾉ容n, fii kulol ngol. ﾆ格in ko hujjaaji ﾉ擁ﾉ擁, immorde ka Joomi maa, haa e Fir'awna e dental mum, pellet, ﾉ兎en laatike yimﾉ兎 faasiqiiﾉ兎""."
  28,33,"O maaki: ""Joomi am, mi ittiino wonkii e maﾉ橡兎, miﾉ熔 huli nde ﾉ兎 mbarata kam."
  28,34,"Ko musiﾉ遼熔 am on Haaruuna, ﾉ砥ri kam laaﾉ砥de ﾉ容mngal. Immindin-mo e am, ko ballitoo kam, gooﾅ極擁am-mi; miﾉ熔 huli nde ﾉ兎 fennata kam""."
  28,35,"[Alla] daali: ""Min cemmbinirat tere maa ﾉ容n, musiﾉ遼熔 maa on, Min mbaﾉ預na on hujja (e cemmbe); ﾉ兎 hewtirtaa on ﾉ擁ﾉ熔, sabu aayeeje Amen ﾉ容 [Min nuli e] mo'on, e ﾉ兎n jokkuﾉ兎 on foolﾉ兎""."
  28,36,"Nde Muusaa addunoo e maﾉ橡兎 aayeeje Amen ﾉ容n ﾉ殿nnguﾉ容, ﾉ兎 mbi'i: ""ﾆ隔m wonaani, si wonaa mbilewu fekindaangu. Min naniraani ﾉ蓉m baabiraaﾉ兎 amen adinooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n""."
  28,37,"Muusaa maaki: ""Ko Joomi am ﾉ砥ri anndude on arduﾉ熔 e peewal, immorde to makko, e on mo battane moﾆｴﾆｴe woodani ka La'akara. Pellet, O malnataa tooﾃｱooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n""."
  28,38,"Fir'awna wi'i: ""eey mon dental, mi anndanaa on deweteeﾉ熔, si wonaa min. Eey ma yo Haamaana, huﾉ橡妬nanam [yiite] e loopal ngal, mahiranaa kam huﾉ兎ere toownde, no gasa ka mi ﾆｴellitoo e Deweteeﾉ熔 Muusaa On; tawde miﾉ熔 sikki mo e fenooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n""."
  28,39,"O townitii ka leydi, kaﾅ橘o e koneeli makko ﾉ擁n, ko aldaa e goonga. ﾆ‘ cikki won'de ﾉ兎 ruttitetaako ka Amen."
  28,40,"Men nanngi mo, kaﾅ橘o e koneeli makko ﾉ擁n, Min mbugii ﾉ兎 ka maayo. Tasko, ko honno battane tooﾃｱﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n mba'unoo."
  28,41,"Min mbaﾉ擁 ﾉ兎 ardiiﾉ兎, noddoo ﾉ兎 e Yiite. ﾃ疎nde Darngal, ﾉ兎 walletaake."
  28,42,"Min njokkintiniri ﾉ兎 ka aduna ﾉ熔o, kuddi. ﾃ疎lnde Darngal, ko ﾉ兎 jiyaaﾉ兎 e woﾉ遼擁ntinoyteeﾉ兎 [e yurmeende Alla]."
  28,43,"Gooﾅ極擁i Min ngokkii Muusaa Deftere nden, ﾉ殿awo nde Min kalkunoo gire arane ﾉ容n, ko nde ndayginorde yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, e peewal e yurmeende. Mbelejo'o, ﾉ兎 mbaajitorat."
  28,44,"A tawanooka ka senngo hiirnaange, fewndo Min mbahyinnoo e Muusaa yamiroore nden, a jeyanooka kadi e seediiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  28,45,"Kono Minen ngoni ni tagkﾉ兎 gire, duuﾉ妬 maﾉ橡兎 juuti. A hoﾉ預ano kadi e yimﾉ兎 Madyana ﾉ兎n, haﾉ預 janngana ﾉ兎 Aayeeje Amen; ko Minen ngoni nulﾉ兎."
  28,46,"A tawanooka ka senngo Fello Tuuri, fewndo Min noddunoo; ko yurmeende immorde ka Joomi maa [woni ko Min nulir-maa], fii no njeertiniraa yimﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 reentinoowo araali e maﾉ橡兎, ado maaﾉ預, mbelejo'o, ﾉ兎 mbaajitoto."
  28,47,"Si wonaano fii yo lepte yanir e maﾉ橡兎, sabu ko juuﾉ容 maﾉ橡兎 ardini, ﾉ兎 wi'ayno: ""Joomi amen, ko haﾉ溶o imminaa Nulaaﾉ熔 e amen? Min njokka nun aayeeje Maa ﾉ容n, men njeyee e gooﾅ極擁mﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n""."
  28,48,"Nde o addirannooﾉ兎 goonga kan, immorde ka amen, ﾉ兎 mb'i: ""Ko haﾉ溶o o okkee yeru ko Muusaa okkanoo kon?"" Kere ﾉ兎 njeddaano ko Muusaa okkanoo kon ko adii? ﾆ‘ mbi'i'i: ""Ko bileeji ﾉ擁ﾉ擁, ﾉ擁 no wallindira!"" ﾆ‘ mbi'i kadi: ""Ko min yedduﾉ兎 fof e mun""."
  28,49,"Maaku: ""ngadee deftere immorde ka Alla, hara hende ﾉ砥ri ﾉ容e ﾉ擁ﾉ擁 feewde, mi jokkaynde, si on laatike goongunﾉ兎""."
  28,50,"Si ﾉ兎 njaabaaki ma, anndu ko mbeleeﾉ容 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎 njokkata. Ko hommbo ﾉ砥ri majjude ﾉ砥ri oon jokkirﾉ熔 mbeleeﾉ容 mun, ko aldaa e peewal immorde ka Alla? Pellet, Alla feewnata yimﾉ兎 tooﾃｱooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  28,51,"Gooﾉ擁i Min hewtinii ﾉ兎 Konngol ngol, mbelejo'o, ﾉ兎 mbaajitora."
  28,52,"ﾆ‘n ﾉ兎 Min ndokki Deftere [Tawreeta] nden, ko adii [Alqur'aana] ndee, ko ﾉ兎 gooﾅ極擁nﾉ兎 nde."
  28,53,"Si nde janngaama e dow maﾉ橡兎, ﾉ兎 mbi'a: ""Min ngooﾅ極擁nii nde. Ko nde goonga immorde ka Joomi amen. Pellet min woniino jebbiliiﾉ兎, ado mayre""."
  28,54,"ﾆ‘en ﾉ熔n, ﾉ兎 jonniroyte njoﾉ電i maﾉ橡兎 ndin, laabi ﾉ擁ﾉ擁, sabu ko ﾉ兎 muﾃｱinoo kon, heﾉ兎 nduﾃｱiraynoo moﾆｴﾆｴere nden, bone on, e hu'unde nde Min ngarsiki ﾉ兎 nden, heﾉ兎 nafqa."
  28,55,"Si ﾉ兎 nanii meerente, ﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉urnoo e ﾉ蓉m, ﾉ兎 mbi'a: ""Ko minen golle amen ngoodani, ko onon kadi golle mon nhoodani. Kisal wonii e mo'on. Min ﾉ預ﾉ橡殿taa wonndugol e majjuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n""."
  28,56,"Pellet, an (Nulaaﾉ熔), a feewnata mo njiﾉ遼預a; kono Alla no feewna on Mo O muuyi. Ko Kaﾅ橘o ﾉ砥ri anndude feewﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  28,57,"ﾆ‘ mbi'i: ""Si min njokkidii peewal ngal e maa, men biftete ka leydi amen"". E Min hoﾉ擁niraali ﾉ兎 e nokku horminaaﾉ熔, koolniiﾉ熔, mo dimﾉ容 noone kaka addetee e mun, arsike immorde ka Amen? Si ko woni, ko ﾉ砥ri ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉de e maﾉ橡兎, ﾉ兎 nganndaa."
  28,58,"ﾆ隔uﾉ擁i ko Min kakli, e yimﾉ兎 ca'e, bewrunooﾉ兎 nguuree mum, e homo non galleeji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n, koﾉ擁raaka ﾉ殿awo maﾉ橡兎, si wonaa seeﾉ預. Min laatii wonn'de ronooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎en."
  28,59,"Joomi maa siforaali won'de kalkoowo yimﾉ兎 ca'e, haa O immina e leﾃｱol maﾉ橡兎ﾉ容n, Nulaaﾉ熔, ko janngana ﾉ兎 aayeeje Amen ﾉ容n. Min siforaali kadi kalkugol yimﾉ兎 ca'e, si wonaa hara yimﾉ兎 majje ko tooﾃｱuﾉ兎."
  28,60,"Kala ko ngokkaﾉ熔n e hu'unde, ko dakamme nguurndam aduna e cuﾉ預ari mun; ko ko woni ka Alla kon, ﾉ砥ri moﾆｴﾆｴude, woni kadi ko luttata. E on haqqiltaa?"
  28,61,"Eey mon Min podi fodaari moﾆｴﾆｴuri, ndi o hawrata e mu'un, wa'ata wa on mo Min ndakmitiri dakamme nguurndam aduna, refti hara kaﾅ橘o on, ﾃ疎lnde Darngal, ko e tawneteeﾉ兎 (ka Yiite) ﾉ兎n o jeyaa?"
  28,62,"ﾃ疎nde O noddoyta ﾉ兎, O wi'a: ""Ko hoﾉ熔 kafidaaﾉ擁 am, ﾉ擁n ﾉ擁 ngaaﾆｴoratnoﾉ熔n woni?"""
  28,63,"ﾆ‘n ﾉ兎 Konngol jojji e Mu'um wi'a: ""Joomi amen, ko ﾉ兎e ngoni ko min bewinnoo. Min bewinirno ﾉ兎, wano men bewirnoo. Min daﾉ溶dinike e Maaﾉ預. Wonaa minen ﾉ兎 ndewatnoo""."
  28,64,"[ﾆ‘] mb'anee: ""Noddee non kafidaaﾉ擁 mon ﾉ擁n"". ﾆ‘ nodda ﾉ擁, kono ﾉ擁 njaabotaako ﾉ兎. ﾆ‘ nji'a lepte ﾉ容n, (ﾉ兎 njeloo) sinno hara ﾉ兎 peewuno."
  28,65,"ﾃ疎nde O noddoyta ﾉ兎, o wi'a: ""Ko holﾉ蓉m njaabinoﾉ熔n Nulaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n?"""
  28,66,"Lamitorﾉ擁 ﾉ擁n mbumiﾉ預na ﾉ兎 nden ﾃｱande, ﾉ兎 lamndondirtaa."
  28,67,"Si ko tuubuﾉ熔, o gooﾅ極擁ni, o golli moﾆｴﾆｴuﾉ擁, hino hasii ka o jeyee e malaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎en."
  28,68,"Joomi maa no taga ko o muuyi, O suﾉ登o; suﾉ殿gol alanaa ﾉ兎. Senaade woodanii Alla! O toowii e kon ko ﾉ兎 cirkata!"
  28,69,"Joomi maa no anndi ko ﾉ兎rﾉ容 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n cuuﾉ預ta, e kon ko ﾉ兎 peﾃｱﾃｱinta."
  28,70,"Ko Kaﾅ橘o Alla woni, Mo deweteeﾉ熔 alaa, si wanaa Kaﾅ橘o. Ko Kaﾅ橘o jettooje nhoodani aduna e La'akara. Hino woodani Mo ﾃｱaawoore nden. Ko ka Makko rutteteﾉ熔n."
  28,71,"Maaku: ""njeewtee kam, Si Alla waﾉ擁ranii on jemma on, duumiiﾉ熔 haa ﾃ疎nde Darngal, ko deweteeﾉ熔 hommbo, tanaa Alla, addanta on ndayngu? E on nanataa?"""
  28,72,"Maaku: ""njeewtee kam, Si Alla waﾉ擁ranii on ﾃｱalorma on, duumiiﾉ熔 haa ﾃ疎nde Darngal, ko deweteeﾉ熔 hommbo, tanaa Alla, addanta on jemma, mo deeﾆｴoton e mun? E on nji'ataa?"""
  28,73,"Hino jeyaa e yurmeende Makko, O waﾉ擁ranii on jemma e ﾃｱalawma; fii no deeﾆｴiron e (jemma) on, e no ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬ron ( e ﾃｱalawma on), ﾉ砥ral makko, e no mbelajo'o njettiron [Mo] ."
  28,74,"ﾃ疎nde O noddoyta ﾉ兎, O wi'a: ""Ko holto kadidaaﾉ擁(renndidiiﾉ擁) am, ﾉ擁n ﾉ擁n ngaaﾆｴoratnoﾉ熔n ngoni?"""
  28,75,"Min ﾉ熔ofi e kala mofte, seedotooﾉ熔, Min mbi'a: ""ngddee hujjaajji mon ﾉ擁n"". ﾆ‘ ngnndi wonn'de goonga kan, ko Alla woodani; ko ﾉ兎 fekindotonoo kon majjitora ﾉ兎."
  28,76,"Pellet,Qaaruuna ko e yimﾉ兎 Muusaa ﾉ兎n jeyanoo,kono o bewi e maﾉ橡兎.Min ngokki mo ngaluuji tawat-ﾉ擁 coktirﾉ容 mum,no teddana jamaa doolnuﾉ熔.Nde yimﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎en,mbiatno mo:Wata a weltor townitaare.Pellet Alla yiﾉ預a weltortooﾉ兎 toownitaare."
  28,77,"ﾆ蛎ﾉ橡妬r ko Alla okku-maa kon, galle laakare ﾉ容n. Wota a yejjit geﾉ預l maa ngal aduna. Moﾆｴﾆｴir no Alla moﾆｴﾆｴorii non e maaﾉ預. Wata a ﾉ預ﾉ橡砥 bonnugol ka leydi. Anndu pellet, Alla yiﾉ預a bonnooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n""."
  28,78,"O wi'i: ""Ko mi okkiraa ﾉ蓉m, ko e hoore ganndal ngal mi jogii"". E o anndaa wonn'de gooﾅ極擁i Alla kalkiino gire, adiiﾉ兎 mo, ﾉ砥rﾉ兎 doole, ﾉ砥ri mo ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉de jawle? ﾆ‘ lamndoytaake fii bakkaat maﾉ橡兎, kamﾉ兎 bomﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n!"
  28,79,"O yaltitiri e yimﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n, cuﾉ預ari makko ndin. Yiﾉ蓉ﾉ兎 nguurndam aduna ﾉ兎n mbi'i: ""Hara nun min keﾉ殿yno sugu koo ko Qaaruuna okkaa. Kaﾅ橘o on, pellet, ko o jom-geﾉ殿l mawnungal""."
  28,80,"Okkaaﾉ兎 ganndal ﾉ兎n kan mbi'i: ""Ee bone mon! Ko mbarjaari Alla ndin ﾉ砥ri moﾆｴﾆｴannde on gooﾅ極擁nﾉ熔 o golli ko moﾆｴﾆｴi"". Kono hawrataa e ﾉ蓉um, si wonaa muﾃｱﾃｱiiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  28,81,"Min mutindini mo e galle makko ﾉ容n, ka leydi. Fedde woo alanaa mo, ko paaboo mo gaanin Alla, o wonaano paabotooﾉ熔 hoore-mum."
  28,82,"ﾆ‘n yelinooﾉ兎 nokku makko on haﾅ橘i mum, ﾉ兎 mbaﾉ葉i wiide: ""Ee bone! Alla no wertana arsike on, Mo O muuyani e jiyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n, O ﾉ妬ﾉ葉inana [Mo O muuyani]. Si wonaa Alla moﾆｴﾆｴinoo e amen, O mutinayno men. Ee bone! Jaka O malnataa yedduﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n""."
  28,83,"ﾆ各n galle laakara, Min mbaﾉ預nii ﾉ容 ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 yiﾉ預a townitaare ka leydi, wonaa kadi bonnugol. Battane moﾆｴﾆｴe ﾉ容n, ko fii gooﾅ極蓉ﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  28,84,"Kala garduﾉ熔 e moﾆｴﾆｴere, hino woodani mo ko ﾉ砥ri nde moﾆｴﾆｴude; kala kadi garduﾉ熔 e bonannde, (yo o anndu) huuwuﾉ兎 bonﾉ擁 ﾉ擁n yoﾉ兎taake, si wanaa ko ﾉ兎 huuwaynoo kon."
  28,85,"Pellet, jippinﾉ熔 Alqur'aana on e maaﾉ預, ko duttoo-wo ma ka woowaandi maa. Maaku: ""Ko Joomi am ﾉ砥ri anndude arduﾉ熔 e peewal, e gonﾉ熔 e majjere ﾉ殿nngunde""."
  28,86,"A wonaano tamﾆｴininooﾉ熔 jippineede deftere nden e maaﾉ預. Si wonaa tun, ko yurmeende immorde ka Joomi maa. Wota won muk, balloowo heeferﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  28,87,"wota ﾉ兎 palo ma kadi e aayeeje Alla ﾉ容n, ﾉ殿awo ﾉ容 jippineede e maaﾉ預. Noddu (yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n) fa'ade e Joomi maa, wota a won muk, jiyaaﾉ熔 e sirkooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  28,88,"Wota a rewudu e Alla, deweteeﾉ熔 goo. Deweteeﾉ熔 goo alaa, si wonaa Kaﾅ橘o. Hu'unde fof re'ay, si wonaa Jaati Maako Kin. Ko Kaﾅ橘o woodani ﾃｱaawugol; ko ka Makko kadi ndtteteﾉ熔n."
